---
import BaseHead from "../../../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="CHIPS Example | bokken.io" description="Example site for CHIPS (Cookies Having Independent Partitioned State)" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h2>CHIPS example</h2>
      <p>This is an example site of CHIPS. The below Simple map app is a map app (cross-origin). The map app saves the location with Cookie. And the Cookie has <code>Partitioned</code> attribute. So, the UA can save the Cookie. For the blocked example, see <a href="https://exp.bokken.dev/example-of-chips/">another example</a>.</p>

      <h2>Search near your place!!</h2>
      <iframe width="500" height="500" src="https://simple-map-zeta.vercel.app"></iframe>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
